{"tid":390450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡若蓮籲給予空間讓她和家人渡過困難時間","createTime":"2017-09-07T06:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T14:39:59.000Z","uid":48093,"like":8,"dislike":406,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8a16384bd288d5b915f9e81e6ea3788c2a3370","tid":390450,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1352798_1_L_20170907140324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1352798_1_L_20170907140324.jpg&h=6cd1dba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局副局長蔡若蓮長子由擎天半島高處墮下死亡。事發在11時許，警方接報一名20多歲男子倒臥在屋苑平台，送往醫院搶救，其後證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n蔡若蓮透過新聞秘書表示，感謝各界人士關心，希望大家給予空間，讓她和家人渡過這段困難的時期。"},{"pid":"8b6ac47fd4045b64351c5845a2542e3f0dff47da","tid":390450,"uid":3773,"like":406,"dislike":2,"score":404,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/e1aed171ded2bd78cc8dc0e73b594eaf/tumblr_o17frv0cdu1u9u459o1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2Fe1aed171ded2bd78cc8dc0e73b594eaf%2Ftumblr_o17frv0cdu1u9u459o1_500.gif&h=7adeed9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fef692420799e759a95e6579d2a1a3d142a9dabe","tid":390450,"uid":997,"like":277,"dislike":1,"score":276,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:07:02.000Z","msg":"痴撚線, 我等緊東張西望訪問你條仆街既"},{"pid":"d886856ddbcb8be0f66da8596b85200353b1ddca","tid":390450,"uid":79563,"like":172,"dislike":1,"score":171,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:07:04.000Z","msg":"你老母咁邊個比空間香港人呀？<br />\n<br />\n你要空間? 無喎, SORRY"},{"pid":"b76dd8417474d44c5a30c04e429374eea1b74d9f","tid":390450,"uid":103207,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/e1aed171ded2bd78cc8dc0e73b594eaf/tumblr_o17frv0cdu1u9u459o1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2Fe1aed171ded2bd78c